  <h2>Concepts</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Photos</strong> -  get uploaded to the site. Only jpegs are allowed at the moment</li>
    <li><strong>Mediaset</strong> - You organize your photos in a mediaset. You can arrange them in a particular order in a mediaset. </li>
    <li><strong>Tags</strong> - #hashtags will help organize your photos. You can view photos by tags. However, they can't be organized in a particular order</li>
  </ul>
  </div>
