    <h2>Uploading</h2>
    <div class="span6">
      <img src="http://placehold.it/600x200" />
    </div>
    <div class="span5">
      <ul>
        <li>Go to the upload page</li>
        <li>Drop your photos inside the box</li>
        <li>Add descriptions with #hashtags or assign them to a existing/new mediaset</li>
        <li>Upload away</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row-fluid">
    <h2>Organizing</h2>
    <div class="span5">
      <strong>Mediaset</strong>
      <ul>
        <li>Go to your mediaset page</li>
        <li>Create a new mediaset</li>
        <li>Drop photos in the mediaset selection. Arrange them to your liking</li>
        <li>Save and you're done</li>
      </ul>
      <strong>Tags</strong>
      <ul>
        <li>Select the photos that you want to edit</li>
        <li>Add #hashtags to the title or description</li>
        <li>The photos will be tagged automatically</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="span6">
      <img src="http://placehold.it/600x200" />
